channel.title: SKILLER (68 Wc, 59 Fletch)
channel.description:
[size=15pt]Last Updated: May 23, 2007: 10:51 P.M. Central Time[/size]
Hey just started my first ever skiller (Woot!) Im gonna aim for 99 woodcutting, then use all the logs for 99 fletching, then sell everything and get 99 cooking, and work on fishing all the way through. When im done with all those, I might go for 99 fm, just cause its really easy if you have money.
My username is The Nxt God Add me and talk to me, cause i am going to be [b]very[/b] bored doing all of this lol.
Heres pic. (will be updated very frequently.)
[IMG]http://i52.photobucket.com/albums/g28/mjpunk02/62wc.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i52.photobucket.com/albums/g28/mjpunk02/44fish.jpg[/img]
[size=15pt]LOG:[/size] [size=15pt]Day 1:[/size] Got all axes up to mith, and gave 7k to the account from my main. (I figured that 7k would be enough to start to buy bait and stuff) Started woodcutting and got up to 21, then started fishing and got to 15. (that was all, i only played for about an hour and 15 minutes)
[size=15pt]Day 2:[/size] Fished for a long time, got fishing to 43 and cooked while fishing. Got cooking to 40. (also got 10 firemaking just from making fires for cooking :D) While fishing, i was creating this topic and I got a random and died :P. Lost all the money I had on the account, 221 feathers (i was going to use for fishing) around 20 tuna, my harpoon and lobster pot, camo top and normal wizard bottom and hat. Since i was out of money and i had lost my lobster pot and harpoon, i decided to turn to woodcutting, got woodcutting to 30. Starting on willows tomorrow probably.
[size=15pt]Day 3:[/size] Started on willows, got some very fast XP... Got to lvl 55 that day. Got 50k from my main and bought a rune axe, so leveling was really quick from 41 to 50, but now its starting to take a little bit longer. Also, i found 360 feathers on the ground so now i have all the feathers back from when i lost em last night :P Another thing: If you want to get a bunch of willows for really cheap, go to rimmington general store in a F2p World. During the day, ive seen up to 3k logs and they sell for like 10 each.
[size=15pt]Day 4:[/size] Kept cuttin willows, but could only get on after school. Got 57 wc so far. Also my friend who is quitting gave me 800 free willows that i will use for fletching. Finished up on willows for the night at 59 wc, so a good 4 lvls for a school day. Im actually quite satisfied :D
[size=15pt]Day 5:[/size] Another school day, and i didnt think id get much done but i did manage to get 4 levels (from 59 to 63) so far. Although i got 60 wc im staying on willows because you cut them much faster and the exp is MUCH better :D (just for those of you who didnt know that) Started on fishing as wc gets kinda boring after 3 days of doing nothing else, so im workin on fishing now, already got 1 lvl and im gettin off for the night.
Im done logging, im too lazy to keep track of the days, and plus eventually the post will be like UB3R long cuz we'll be up to like 30 days.
Ill just keep posting new pics of the stats.

Not even worth spending the time to bank. I just really care about exp right now, and usually late at night i do cut at draynor because i need to get logs for fletching.
And also i cant really cut much faster than most of the people at draynor. At draynor it takes me 3 Minutes or more to get an inventory of willows, in Rimmington it takes me around a minute and a half and sometimes less.
Once again pretty much i dont really care about money, i Merch whips on my pure and i have 22m on there (i just got hacked 15m 2 weeks ago and already made back 22m just by doing that while pcing)
